original_title: Delbert McClinton: Live from Austin TX
overview: Delbert McClinton, three time Grammy winning blues rocker, rips it up on the Austin City Limits stage during this amazing performance. Delbert McClinton's Live From Austin, Texas, performance includes his classics Givin' It Up For Your Love, I've Got Dreams to Remember, and many more!
title: Delbert McClinton: Live from Austin TX
